{"tid":56051,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人已經進化到香港好少用錢，旅行多用錢？","createTime":"2016-12-27T01:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T22:10:18.000Z","uid":51701,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc42d3a352e41ace6f3b0de129aa676d279c927","tid":56051,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"近年出trip做野/自己玩都出外食豪過香港好多<br />\n買買買 唔想比香港地產佬輪姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東南亞食豪住豪，唔洗飲東江水吸支那廢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去日韓連日用品衣食都買埋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然分好多次買啦（保健品藥係美國gnc amazon)<br />\n<br />\n全家得大電器同傢俬果d 外國買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部mik mij用落安心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多日實惠萬寧有賣mic 仲貴過香港，地產佬我屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果近幾年好少洗錢係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (只限狗鐵狗巴食飯同硬食百佳759坐hx/uo/Amiles）<br />\n不過香港gdp 咁高唔會因為我一個人拉低ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋終於明白水貨狗點解比人歧視都要黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留港消費？ 不了，冇錢冇信心又唔受氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不捐錢 不捐血 少在港消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d53b33e1dfca69eed7705f77e829bab54561cbf","tid":56051,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"我已經由衫去到鞋都係日本買<br />\n日日如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4fd83f00185907868ce38ae02a9ec5e644cc5e","tid":56051,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"除左返工要搭車 食飯都係帶飯 唔想出去食貴飯比人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec16eadca40697803c576c5a7b506e257254ca63","tid":56051,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我已經由衫去到鞋都係日本買<br />\n日日如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連水樽筷子都係，貪佢安全d(安全過日本城中國製仲貴果d掛）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9401395f63717affb3d9fb5af4a5700e360d8b52","tid":56051,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"ios 板冇preview, 有d 錯字希望冇1999"},{"pid":"8694dc06b9747abcab4879b2993571a9541e0649","tid":56051,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"已經進化咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢外國平過香港。<br />\n<br />\n尤其係食，香港唔捨得食嘅，外國就搏命食。"},{"pid":"af84a60391435c527f27bdf7801eee176e98cdc4","tid":56051,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"已經維持左幾年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買親野都外國買"},{"pid":"c8e671df44b5952dc1995b5d1edb2c00b5c07a4e","tid":56051,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經維持左幾年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買親野都外國買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48283c0a5356ff6d33edc159e4bd0425f5c3f55a","tid":56051,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4c8bec4350bc8bb5d94302ac1e9766d6fbe19a","tid":56051,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"935e6bd3a0d8a24d2533ada0c29ba9130a659663","tid":56051,"uid":35920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"同啲蝗蟲黎香港買晒啲日用品奶粉電器一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfecab0eb6cd909057e6e3570ba74bd68929d35a","tid":56051,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"香港有D衫鋪鞋鋪賣既野已經狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為target支那人 taste cheap撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3959fddbc8b6adc513f1cdf06934be7fd19c3ea6","tid":56051,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"家下d鋪頭咪又係淘寶"},{"pid":"e2fcf31d19f602756b1607e6acff908e26c2dec1","tid":56051,"uid":17820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"成班離地撚自命清高 <br />\n有頭髮邊個想做熾哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f1626f892f03e2681e78f41362b90459dc9ce7","tid":56051,"uid":39559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"而家著緊既衫褲鞋都係旅行個時買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5a3bdf0c31ebfdb1b2aa1deeb5c0cdf8ac89e3","tid":56051,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"這是好的"},{"pid":"478c0961a8ea02d97801475fa7c90862665c89bb","tid":56051,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi